      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Plasmids and 293TT cells used for PsV production were kindly provided by John Schiller (National Cancer Institute, Bethesda, MD). Detailed protocols and plasmid maps for this study can be seen at http://home .ccr.cancer.gov/lco/default.asp. HPV-16, HPV-18, HPV-6, and bovine papillomavirus type 1 (BPV-1) PsV were produced according to previously described methods [CITATION_1] ."
